ags=2520263 |title=Listing of Groups and Organizations {{!}} Mason360|website=mason360.gmu.edu|access-date=August 16, 2019}}</ref>\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n!Student Organization\n!Abbr./Letters\n!Religion\n!Denomination or Sect\n!National Affiliation\n!Type\n|-\n|4Corners Christian Fellowship\n|4Corners\n|Christianity\n|\n|\n|Fellowship\n|-\n|Access Islam\n|\n|Islam\n|\n|\n|Academic/Theological\n|-\n|Ahmadiyya Muslim Student Association\n|\n|Islam\n|Ahmadiyya Movement\n|\n|Appreciation & Philosophy\n|-\n|Align Fitness<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://mason360.gmu.edu/alignfitness/home/ |title=Home - Align Fitness {{!}} George Mason University|website=mason360.gmu.edu|access-date=August 16, 2019}}</ref>\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|Sports Ministry Fellowship \n|-\n|Anointed Vessels of Unity\n|AVU\n|Christianity\n|\n|\n|\n|-\n|Apostles Campus Church\n|ACC\n|Christianity\n|Anglican\n|\n|Church\n|-\n|Arise Campus Ministry\n|\n|Christianity\n|[[Christian Church (Disciples of Christ)]], \n[[Episcopal Church (United States)|Episcopal]] ([[Anglicanism|Anglican]]), [[Presbyterian Church (USA)|Presbyterian (USA)]],\n\n[[United Church of Christ]],\n\n[[United Methodist Church|United Methodist]] ([[Wesleyan theology|Wesleyan]])\n|\n|[[Wesley Foundation]], \nCanterbury Club,\n\n[[Presbyterian House]]\n|-\n|Baha'i Club\n|\n|Bah\u00e1'\u00ed Faith\n|\n|Bah\u00e1\u2019\u00ed Campus Ministry \n|\n|-\n|Bridges International\n|\n|[[Christianity]]\n|\n|Bridges International\n|Community Organization \n|-\n|George Mason Catholic Campus Ministry \n(St. Robert Bellarmine Chapel)\n|CCM\n|Christianity\n|[[Catholic Church|Catholic]]\n|Works with the Fellowship of Catholic University Students \n(FOCUS) | [[Catholic campus ministry]]\n|Fellowship & Church\n|-\n|GMU [[Chi Alpha (Christian Fellowship)|Chi Alpha]] \n(Chi Alpha Christian Fellowship)\n|\u03a7\u0391 (GMUXA)\n|Christianity\n|inter-denominational local chapters\n|Chi Alpha Campus Ministries \n([[Assemblies of God USA]]\u2014national affiliate)\n|Fellowshi