z]]\n| 1930\n| [[Smithsonian Institution]] {{coord|38|53|20.74|N|77|1|22.84|W|region:US}}\n| [[Bronze]]\n| 87\u00bd \u00d7 38\u00bd \u00d7 28\u00bd in.\n| Library of Congress<ref name=\"Figure\">{{Cite web| author=Smithsonian | year=1998 | title=Figure (sculpture)  | work=Inventories of American Painting and Sculpture | publisher=Smithsonian | url=http://siris-artinventories.si.edu/ipac20/ipac.jsp?&profile=all&source=~!siartinventories&uri=full=3100001~!5615~!0#focus | accessdate= May 22, 2010}}</ref>\n|\n|-\n| [[Eminent Men of Letters]]\n| [[Frederick Ruckstull]] & [[Herbert Adams (sculptor)|Herbert Adams]]\n| 1894\u201395\n| [[Library of Congress]]\n| [[Granite]]\n| H. 3&nbsp;ft.\n| Library of Congress<ref name=\"Eminent Ben Frankl\">{{Cite web| author=Save Outdoor Sculptures! | year=1993 | title=Eminent Men of Letters: Benjamin Franklin (sculpture)  | work=SOS! | publisher=Smithsonian | url=http://siris-artinventories.si.edu/ipac20/ipac.jsp?&profile=all&source=~!siartinventories&uri=full=3100001~!18500~!0#focus | accessdate= May 22, 2010}}</ref><ref name=\"Eminent Men of Letters: Demosthenes\">{{Cite web| author=Save Outdoor Sculptures! | year=1993 | title=Eminent Men of Letters: Demosthenes (sculpture)  | work=SOS! | publisher=Smithsonian | url=http://siris-artinventories.si.edu/ipac20/ipac.jsp?&profile=all&source=~!siartinventories&uri=full=3100001~!15754~!0#focus | accessdate= May 26, 2010}}</ref><ref name=\"Eminent Men of Letters: Dante\">{{Cite web| author=Save Outdoor Sculptures! | year=1993 | title=Eminent Men of Letters: Dante (sculpture)  | work=SOS! | publisher=Smithsonian | url=http://siris-artinventories.si.edu/ipac20/ipac.jsp?&profile=all&source=~!siartinventories&uri=full=3100001~!359698~!0#focus | accessdate= May 26, 2010}}</ref><ref name=\"Eminent Men of Letters: Scott\">{{Cite web| author=Save Outdoor Sculptures! | year=1993 | title=Eminent Men of Letters: Scott (sculpture)  | work=SOS! | publisher=Smithsonian | url=http://siris-artinventories.si