iculture Pediment: Fruit\">{{Cite web| author=Save Outdoor Sculptures! | year=1993 | title=Department of Agriculture Pediment: Fruit (sculpture)  | work=SOS! | publisher=Smithsonian | url=http://siris-artinventories.si.edu/ipac20/ipac.jsp?&profile=all&source=~!siartinventories&uri=full=3100001~!377922~!0#focus | accessdate= May 26, 2010}}</ref><ref name=\"Department of Agriculture Pediment: Forestry\">{{Cite web| author=Save Outdoor Sculptures! | year=1993 | title=Department of Agriculture Pediment: Forestry (sculpture)  | work=SOS! | publisher=Smithsonian | url=http://siris-artinventories.si.edu/ipac20/ipac.jsp?&profile=all&source=~!siartinventories&uri=full=3100001~!377925~!0#focus | accessdate= May 26, 2010}}</ref>\n|\n|-\n| [[Scenes from American Industry]]\n| [[Otto Eggers]]\n| 1956\n| [[Dirksen Senate Office Building]]\n| [[Bronze]]\n| 5 panels. Each: Approx. 3\u00bd&nbsp;ft. square.\n| Dirksen Senate Office Building<ref name=\"Scenes from American Industry\">{{Cite web| author=University of Delaware | year=1985 | title=Scenes from American Industry (sculpture)  | work=SOS! | publisher=Smithsonian | url=http://siris-artinventories.si.edu/ipac20/ipac.jsp?&profile=all&source=~!siartinventories&uri=full=3100001~!16739~!0#focus | accessdate= May 22, 2010}}</ref>\n|\n|-\n| [[Eagle Pediment]]\n| [[Ulysses Ricci]]\n| 1956\n| [[Dirksen Senate Office Building]]\n{{Coord|38|53|42|N|77|2|11|W|region:US}}\n| [[Marble]]\n| D 4&nbsp;ft.\n| Dirksen Senate Office Building<ref name=\"Eagle Pediment\">{{Cite web| author=Save Outdoor Sculptures! | year=1993 | title=Eagle Pediment (sculpture)  | work=SOS! | publisher=Smithsonian | url=http://siris-artinventories.si.edu/ipac20/ipac.jsp?&profile=all&source=~!siartinventories&uri=full=3100001~!377316~!0#focus | accessdate= May 8, 2010}}</ref>\n|\n|-\n| [[Olive Risley Seward (Cavanaugh)|Olive Risley Seward]]\n| [[John Cavanaugh (sculptor)|John Cavanaugh]]\n| 1971\n| 601 N. Carolina Ave, S.E.\n{{Coord|38|53|11|N|76|59|54|W|region:US}}