ea | publisher=dcMemorial | url=http://www.dcmemorials.com/index_indiv0000242.htm | accessdate= June 1, 2010}}</ref>\n|[[File:Walter Jones Cong Cemetery Ward 6.JPG|120px]]\n|-\n| [[General Alexander Macomb Monument]]\n| Unknown\n| 1941\n| [[Congressional Cemetery]] \u2013 NE Section, Range 55, Site 147\n| [[Marble]] & [[Granite]]\n| Obelisk: approx. H. 78 in.; Shaft: approx. 22 \u00d7 40 \u00d7 40 in.; Base: approx. 14 \u00d7 42 \u00d7 42 in.\n| [[Congressional Cemetery|Association for the Preservation of Historic Congressional Cemetery]]<ref name=\"General Alexander Macomb Monument\">{{Cite web| author=Save Outdoor Sculpture! | year=1994 | title=General Alexander Macomb Monument (sculpture)  | work=SOS! | publisher=Smithsonian | url=http://siris-artinventories.si.edu/ipac20/ipac.jsp?&profile=all&source=~!siartinventories&uri=full=3100001~!349612~!0#focus | accessdate= May 30, 2010}}</ref>\n|[[File:Macomb grave CC.JPG|120px]]\n|-\n| [[Taza (Burial Marker)]]\n| [[Doug Hyde]]\n| 1971\n| [[Congressional Cemetery]]\n| [[Rock (geology)|Stone]] & [[Granite]]\n| Sculpture: approx. 1&nbsp;ft. 6 in. \u00d7 1&nbsp;ft. 6 in. \u00d7 8 in.; Base: approx. 4 in. \u00d7 2&nbsp;ft. \u00d7 10 in.\n| [[Congressional Cemetery|Association for the Preservation of Historic Congressional Cemetery]]<ref name=\"TAZA (Burial Marker)\">{{Cite web| author=Save Outdoor Sculpture! | year=1994 | title=TAZA (Burial Marker)(sculpture)  | work=SOS! | publisher=Smithsonian | url=http://siris-artinventories.si.edu/ipac20/ipac.jsp?&profile=all&source=~!siartinventories&uri=full=3100001~!323774~!0#focus | accessdate= May 27, 2010}}</ref>\n|[[File:Chief Taza at CC no QR.JPG|120px]]\n|-\n| [[Latrobe Cenotaphs]]\n| [[Benjamin Henry Latrobe]]\n| 1816\u20131877\n| [[Congressional Cemetery]]\n| [[Sandstone]]\n| Over 100. Each: H. 4\u00bd&nbsp;ft.\n| [[Congressional Cemetery|Association for the Preservation of Historic Congressional Cemetery]]<ref name=\"Latrobe Cenotaphs\">{{Cite web| author=Save Outdoor Sculp