ey]]\n| 2004\n| [[Potomac Electric Power Company|PEPCO Headquarters]]\n|\n|\n| [[Washington Metro]]<ref name=\"DCMap\"/>]<ref name=\"PublicArtinDCSelect\"/>\n| [[File:PEPCO Building.JPG|120px]]\n|-\n| [[Air Shaft Tunnel]]\n| [[Val E. Lewton]]\n| 1992\n| H St. N.W. & 3rd St. N.W.\n|\n|\n| <ref name=\"DCMap\"/>\n|\n|-\n| [[Of the People (Daley)|Of the People]]\n| [[Egon Daley]]\n| 1995\n| [[One Judiciary Square]], 441 4th St., N.W.\n|\n|\n| <ref name=\"DCMap\"/>\n|\n|-\n| [[Quadrature Nimbii]]\n| [[Val E. Lewton]]\n| 1996\n| [[One Judiciary Square]], 441 4th St., N.W.\n|\n|\n| <ref name=\"DCMap\"/>\n|\n|-\n| [[Hopscotch Bridge]]\n| [[Val E. Lewton]]\n| 1997\n| H Street Bridge, [[H Street (Washington, D.C.)|H St.]] between N Capitol 7 1st St.\n|\n|\n| <ref name=\"DCMap\"/>\n|\n|-\n| [[Earth Point (Brown)|Earth Point]]\n| [[Karen Brown (artist)|Karen Brown]]\n| 2003\n| Office of Homeland Security, 2720 Martin Luther King Jr. Ave., S.E.\n|\n|\n| <ref name=\"DCMap\"/>\n|\n|-\n| [[Ready (Wegman)|Ready]]\n| [[William Wegman (photographer)|William Wegman]]\n|\n| [[L'Enfant Plaza (WMATA station)|L'Enfant Plaza Metro Station]]\n|\n|\n| <ref name=\"DCMap\"/>\n|\n|-\n| [[Southwest Gateway]]\n| [[G. Byron Peck]]\n| 2008\n| 12th St Tunnels, Maine Ave SW & 12th St, S.W.\n|\n| 2400 Sq. Ft.\n| <ref name=\"DCMap\"/><ref name=\"GByronPeck\">{{Cite web| author=City Arts | year=2007 | title=G. Byron Peck  | work=Board of Directors | publisher=City ARts | url=http://cityartsdc.org/about/board_gpeck.php | accessdate= May 31, 2010}}</ref>\n|\n|-\n| [[Dragon Gate (Crawford)|Dragon Gate]]\n| [[Andrew T. Crawford]]\n| 2007\n| Alley, between 603 and 604 H St., N.W.\n|\n|\n| <ref name=\"DCMap\"/>\n|\n|-\n| [[Balance (Billig)|Balance]]\n| [[Marcia Billig]]\n| 2002\n| 13th St., N.E. & Constitution Ave., N.E. & Tennessee Ave., N.E.\n| [[Bronze]]\n|\n| <ref name=\"DCMap\"/>\n|\n|-\n| [[Ocean Piece]]\n| [[Jorge Martin (artist)|Jorge Martin]]\n| 1995\n| [[Archives (WMATA station)|Archives station]]\n|